# ============================================
# HOW TO GET THESE VALUES
# ============================================

# AZURE POSTGRESQL:
# 1. Go to Azure Portal → PostgreSQL Flexible Servers
# 2. Select your server
# 3. Go to "Connection strings" in the left menu
# 4. Copy the connection details

# AZURE BLOB STORAGE:
# 1. Go to Azure Portal → Storage Accounts
# 2. Select your storage account
# 3. Go to "Access keys" in the left menu
# 4. Copy "Storage account name", "Key", and "Connection string"

# AZURE AD B2C:
# 1. Go to Azure Portal → Azure AD B2C
# 2. Go to "App registrations"
# 3. Select your app or create a new one
# 4. Copy "Application (client) ID"
# 5. Go to "Certificates & secrets" → Create new client secret
# 6. Go to "User flows" → Create or select your sign-up/sign-in flow

# NEXTAUTH_SECRET:
# Generate a random secret with:
# openssl rand -base64 32
# Or use: https://generate-secret.vercel.app/32
